 * @author  Bill Lucas
 * @date    2015-Jan-29
 *
 *  2015-Mar-12 Bill Lucas
 *      cleaned up for Manulife installation; updated for OrchestraCMS Winter '15 compatibility
 *
 *  2015-Jan-29 Bill Lucas
 *      original
